I '''Gandhiskri Sikheriya''' [[Zvolen]]ostar si oxto bershenge [[romani]] Sikheriya (Gemnazeyum); lako anav si katar o [[Mahatma Gandhi]], butshundo [[desi]] andar o 20to [[shelbersh]]. Kathe, shirdindoy [[Deshtoenya]] [[2004]] [[bersh]]estar, siklen Shave tay Rakle (e palutne si opretele 30% [http://www1.umn.edu/humanrts/hrcommittee/slovakia2005.html]). Le siklovne, avri la Sikheriyatar, beshen ando Shtudentengro kher (Universiteto).

Le siklyaripnaske [[Chhiba|Chiba]] si [[romani]], [[Slovaika|Slovayka]] tay  [[Anglezikani]]. Siklel pes vi o [[romanipen]], o Romano sanskritipen tay puranipen.

